			<description><![CDATA[Kirandeep: As with all practices – and meditation is apractice – you have to put the time and energy into it.  Sometimes we sit to do meditation, but don’treally focus and so we only get a minimal benefit.  When we sit in the awareness of being a spiritualbeing, a peaceful soul, we can detach a little and understand that we are thecreator of our thoughts and put a ‘full stop’ to negative thoughts that lead tosorrow and frustration and create the thoughts we want to; thoughts of peaceand harmony, thoughts of good wishes for the self and others.  Whatever thoughts we create, so will be ourfeelings.   Also remember that your twolittle babies are souls also, and actually belong to God, and so with thisrecognition, you can detach a little and give them pure spiritual love and careand let go of feelings of attachment which will cause stress and sorrow.  Hope this helps.]]></description>
